gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Celtics 113, Hawks 103
gameRecap.excerpt: The Celtics defeated the Hawks, 113-103. Jayson Tatum recorded 34 points, nine rebounds, and four assists for the Celtics, with Jaylen Brown adding 21 points and seven rebounds in the victory. Trae Young tallied 33 points, seven assists, and five rebounds for the Hawks in the defeat. The Celtics improve to 13-4 in the regular season, while the Hawks fall to 8-8.
